Sentencas: In the present work, cathode materials of Ba0.5Sr0.5(Co1-xMgx)0.2Fe0.8O3 system (x = 0, 0.2, 0.4, 0.6, 0.8, 1) have been produced and the effect of magnesium (Mg) doping level on cathode performance with Gadolinium doped Cerium (GDC) electrolyte was investigated.
Titulo: Development of BSCMF system of cathode materials and fabrication of symmetrical cell (BSCMF/GDC/BSCMF) for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: The polarisation resistance (RP) for cathode symmetric cells was measured from 600 degrees C to 700 degrees C under open circuit state.
Titulo: Development of BSCMF system of cathode materials and fabrication of symmetrical cell (BSCMF/GDC/BSCMF) for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: At 700 degrees C, the polarisation resistance of BSCF is 13.96 ohm-cm2 and with the addition of Mg it has decreased to 5.17 ohm-cm2.
Titulo: Development of BSCMF system of cathode materials and fabrication of symmetrical cell (BSCMF/GDC/BSCMF) for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: Further increase in the Mg concentration decreased the polarisation resistance up to 0.34 ohm-cm2, which is the minimum value obtained in the composition BSCMF8.
Titulo: Development of BSCMF system of cathode materials and fabrication of symmetrical cell (BSCMF/GDC/BSCMF) for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: It is observed that charge transfer (CT) is more in the case of Mg-rich compositions.
Titulo: Development of BSCMF system of cathode materials and fabrication of symmetrical cell (BSCMF/GDC/BSCMF) for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: With the increase of magnesium concentration in the cathode, RP value was observed as decreased.
Titulo: Development of BSCMF system of cathode materials and fabrication of symmetrical cell (BSCMF/GDC/BSCMF) for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: This is due to the high oxygen permeation flux behaviour of magnesium, which is in the B-site of the cathode.
Titulo: Development of BSCMF system of cathode materials and fabrication of symmetrical cell (BSCMF/GDC/BSCMF) for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications

Sentencas: The coefficient of thermal expansion (CTE) of BSCF is measured to be 22.1 x 10-6/K and decreased to 17.45 x 10-6/K with Mg addition in the composition to BSCMF8, due to the constant oxidation state of Mg by which it suppressed the chemical expansion caused by Co.
Titulo: Development of BSCMF system of cathode materials and fabrication of symmetrical cell (BSCMF/GDC/BSCMF) for low temperature solid oxide fuel cell applications
